reviewText: wonderful.  arrived so fast!  and the show is great.  thank you so much.

For fans of classic tv comedy, this dvd will be a welcome addition to a collection! This is good for a starting 'sample' of the
series...but eventually, I will have to purchase the complete series DVD set. The lead actors, Eve Arden and Kaye Ballard, are
excellent in this series!
It will make a nice Christmas gift for someone who like the show.
